2
00:00:31,368 --> 00:00:34,118
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Izinkan kami menceritakan
sebuah kisah kuno padamu...</i></font>

3
00:00:34,528 --> 00:00:37,845
<font color="#ffff00"><i>...dan kami ingin tahu,
Seberapa tahukah kamu.</i></font>

4
00:00:38,820 --> 00:00:41,459
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Dahulu kala, Ada dua kerajaan...</i></font>

5
00:00:41,561 --> 00:00:43,461
<font color="#ffff00"><i>...yang saling bermusuhan.</i></font>

6
00:00:43,557 --> 00:00:46,490
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Terlalu besarnya permusuhan itu...</i></font>

7
00:00:46,692 --> 00:00:49,110
<font color="#ffff00"><i>...banyak bilang, Hanya pahlawan sejati...</i></font>

8
00:00:49,284 --> 00:00:52,292
<font color="#ffff00"><i>...ataukah penjahat terkejam
yang bisa menyatukan mereka.</i></font>

9
00:00:52,476 --> 00:00:55,756
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Kerajaan pertama, Hidup
orang-orang seperti kita.</i></font>

10
00:00:55,846 --> 00:00:59,444
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Dipimpin oleh raja yang angkuh dan serakah.</i></font>

11
00:01:00,208 --> 00:01:02,917
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Mereka selalu tak merasa
puas dan selalu iri...</i></font>

12
00:01:03,072 --> 00:01:05,819
<font color="#ffff00"><i>...akan kemakmuran serta
keindahan kerajaan sebelah.</i></font>

13
00:01:06,285 --> 00:01:08,496
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Kerajaan kedua, Kerajaan Moors...</i></font>

14
00:01:08,549 --> 00:01:12,955
<font color="#ffff00"><i>...hiduplah segala jenis makhluk
yang unik dan luar biasa.</i></font>

15
00:01:13,485 --> 00:01:16,290
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Mereka tak butuh raja atau ratu...</i></font>

16
00:01:16,330 --> 00:01:18,551
<font color="#ffff00"><i>...karena mereka saling
percaya satu sama lain.</i></font>

17
00:01:20,417 --> 00:01:24,329
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Di sebuah pohon besar di
tebing besar di Kerajaan Moors...</i></font>

18
00:01:24,367 --> 00:01:26,432
<font color="#ffff00"><i>...hiduplah seorang makhluk.</i></font>

19
00:01:26,510 --> 00:01:29,544
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Kau bisa sebut dia gadis.</i></font>

20
00:01:30,360 --> 00:01:33,360
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Tapi dia bukanlah gadis biasa.</i></font>

21
00:01:33,609 --> 00:01:36,313
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Dia seorang peri.</i></font>

22
00:02:04,035 --> 00:02:05,919
<font color="#ffff00">Sudah tidak patah lagi.</font>

23
00:02:06,626 --> 00:02:10,597
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Dan namanya Maleficent.</i></font>

24
00:02:19,988 --> 00:02:23,762
<font color="#ffff00">Pagi, Tn. Chanterelle!
Aku menyukai topimu.</font>

25
00:02:29,363 --> 00:02:31,600
<font color="#ffff00">Jangan!
Jangan lempar!</font>

26
00:02:35,793 --> 00:02:38,667
<font color="#ffff00">Kau meleset!</font>

27
00:02:39,149 --> 00:02:40,739
<font color="#ffff00">Pagi. /
Pagi.</font>

28
00:02:48,852 --> 00:02:50,848
<font color="#ffff00">Aku menyukai gerakan kalian.</font>

29
00:03:07,289 --> 00:03:09,749
<font color="#ffff00">Kenapa ini? /
Penjaga perbatasan--</font>

30
00:03:09,776 --> 00:03:12,053
<font color="#ffff00">Mengapa kau?
Aku yang harusnya bicara.</font>

31
00:03:12,072 --> 00:03:15,018
<font color="#ffff00">Ada aturan, Flittle.
Aku sekarang, Kau yang berikutnya.</font>

32
00:03:15,100 --> 00:03:17,004
<font color="#ffff00">Penjaga perbatasan-- /
Kau suka terakhir kali...</font>

33
00:03:17,079 --> 00:03:19,229
<font color="#ffff00">...jadi, Sekarang aku,
Baru berikutnya Thistlewit.</font>

34
00:03:19,339 --> 00:03:20,731
<font color="#ffff00">Ada apa?</font>

35
00:03:20,789 --> 00:03:23,598
<font color="#ffff00">Oke! /
Ah, Terima kasih!</font>

36
00:03:23,700 --> 00:03:25,290
<font color="#ffff00">Maleficent, Penjaga perbatasan--</font>

37
00:03:25,316 --> 00:03:29,020
<font color="#ffff00">Mereka menemukan manusia
pencuri di Kolam Permata!</font>

38
00:03:30,388 --> 00:03:31,894
<font color="#ffff00">Maafkan aku.</font>

39
00:03:36,610 --> 00:03:39,313
<font color="#ffff00">Dia selalu terburu-buru
dengan sayap besarnya itu.</font>

40
00:03:39,363 --> 00:03:43,150
<font color="#ffff00">Manusia.
Kuharap takkan terjadi perang lagi.</font>

41
00:03:54,529 --> 00:03:56,424
<font color="#ffff00">Aku tak takut.</font>

42
00:03:56,750 --> 00:04:00,696
<font color="#ffff00">Lagian, Aku belum pernah
ketemu manusia sedekat ini.</font>

43
00:04:00,827 --> 00:04:02,534
<font color="#ffff00">Keluarlah dari situ!</font>

44
00:04:02,783 --> 00:04:05,403
<font color="#ffff00">Tak mau!
Mereka ingin membunuhku!</font>

45
00:04:05,639 --> 00:04:08,550
<font color="#ffff00">Selain itu, Tampangnya mengerikan.</font>

46
00:04:09,385 --> 00:04:11,451
<font color="#ffff00">Kata-katamu kejam sekali!</font>

47
00:04:11,563 --> 00:04:15,625
<font color="#ffff00">Jangan dengarkan dia, Balthazar.
Kau sangat tampan.</font>

48
00:04:17,558 --> 00:04:21,595
<font color="#ffff00">Mencuri adalah perbuatan buruk,
Tapi kami tak menghukumnya dengan membunuh.</font>

49
00:04:22,007 --> 00:04:25,885
<font color="#ffff00">Keluarlah dari situ, Sekarang!</font>

50
00:04:37,306 --> 00:04:39,337
<font color="#ffff00">Apa kau orang dewasa?</font>

51
00:04:39,694 --> 00:04:41,221
<font color="#ffff00">Belum.</font>

52
00:04:41,632 --> 00:04:44,507
<font color="#ffff00">Ternyata dia hanyalah anak laki-laki.</font>

53
00:04:44,546 --> 00:04:48,488
<font color="#ffff00">Dan kau hanyalah anak perempuan.
Kurasa...</font>

54
00:04:48,498 --> 00:04:50,028
<font color="#ffff00">Siapa namamu?</font>

55
00:04:50,071 --> 00:04:53,610
<font color="#ffff00">Namaku Stefan.
Kau siapa?</font>

56
00:04:53,688 --> 00:04:55,618
<font color="#ffff00">Aku Maleficent.</font>

57
00:04:58,645 --> 00:05:00,641
<font color="#ffff00">Ya, Benar.</font>

58
00:05:01,118 --> 00:05:02,914
<font color="#ffff00">Kau harus mengembalikannya.</font>

59
00:05:03,293 --> 00:05:04,946
<font color="#ffff00">Kembalikan apa?</font>

60
00:05:25,460 --> 00:05:29,305
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Kalau tahu kau akan buang itu,
Aku takkan berikan padamu.</i></font>

61
00:05:29,346 --> 00:05:31,077
<font color="#ffff00">Aku tak membuangnya.</font>

62
00:05:31,084 --> 00:05:34,731
<font color="#ffff00">Aku membawanya pulang,
Sama seperti padamu.</font>

63
00:05:38,587 --> 00:05:42,729
<font color="#ffff00">Suatu hari nanti, Aku akan
tinggal di istana sana.</font>

64
00:05:46,657 --> 00:05:48,530
<font color="#ffff00">Kau tinggal di mana sekarang?</font>

65
00:05:49,671 --> 00:05:51,573
<font color="#ffff00">Di lumbung.</font>

66
00:05:51,613 --> 00:05:53,745
<font color="#ffff00">Jadi orang tuamu petani?</font>

67
00:05:53,890 --> 00:05:56,592
<font color="#ffff00">Orang tuaku telah meninggal.</font>

68
00:05:58,779 --> 00:06:00,649
<font color="#ffff00">Aku juga.</font>

69
00:06:03,935 --> 00:06:06,132
<font color="#ffff00">Sampai jumpa nanti.</font>

70
00:06:06,145 --> 00:06:08,782
<font color="#ffff00">Sebaiknya kau tak kembali ke sini.</font>

71
00:06:08,824 --> 00:06:10,663
<font color="#ffff00">Tidak aman berada di sini.</font>

72
00:06:13,747 --> 00:06:17,785
<font color="#ffff00">Dan kalau aku menolak,
Apa kau akan ada di sini?</font>

73
00:06:18,871 --> 00:06:20,473
<font color="#ffff00">Mungkin.</font>

74
00:06:23,122 --> 00:06:24,927
<font color="#ffff00">Ada apa?</font>

75
00:06:24,964 --> 00:06:28,166
<font color="#ffff00">Cincinmu!
Besi membakar para peri.</font>

76
00:06:28,213 --> 00:06:30,046
<font color="#ffff00">Maafkan aku.</font>

77
00:06:36,785 --> 00:06:38,859
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Aku menyukai sayapmu.</i></font>

78
00:06:40,503 --> 00:06:44,009
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Maleficent berpikir mengapa
Stefan membuat cincinnya.</i></font>

79
00:06:44,051 --> 00:06:46,856
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Stefan, yang hidupnya sangat sederhana.</i></font>

80
00:06:46,898 --> 00:06:49,875
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Hanya agar tangannya bisa disentuh lagi.</i></font>

81
00:06:49,911 --> 00:06:52,655
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Dan hatinya tergerak.</i></font>

82
00:06:52,926 --> 00:06:56,632
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Mengapa bocah pencuri yang
ingin mencuri permata...</i></font>

83
00:06:57,078 --> 00:07:00,021
<font color="#ffff00"><i>...malah mencuri sesuatu
yang lebih berharga!</i></font>

84
00:07:00,058 --> 00:07:01,928
<font color="#ffff00">Maleficent!</font>

85
00:07:04,076 --> 00:07:05,981
<font color="#ffff00">Maleficent!</font>

86
00:07:10,516 --> 00:07:14,151
<font color="#ffff00">Setelah sekian lama, Lihat
siapa yang kembali!</font>

87
00:07:15,515 --> 00:07:17,613
<font color="#ffff00">Kupikir ini pantas.</font>

88
00:07:18,140 --> 00:07:21,118
<font color="#ffff00">Jadi, Kau buat apa untuk bersenang-senang?</font>

89
00:07:30,161 --> 00:07:34,199
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Stefan dan Maleficent jadi
teman seperti yang lainnya.</i></font>

90
00:07:34,876 --> 00:07:38,519
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Dan terlihat dari mereka seperti...</i></font>

91
00:07:38,548 --> 00:07:42,987
<font color="#ffff00"><i>...kebencian antara manusia
dan peri terlupakan.</i></font>

92
00:07:43,860 --> 00:07:48,264
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Dan lama-kelamaan, persahabatan
mereka mengarah ke hubungan spesial.</i></font>

93
00:07:55,276 --> 00:07:57,695
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Dan pada ulang tahun ke-16-nya...</i></font>

94
00:07:57,722 --> 00:08:00,274
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Stefan memberi hadiah pada Maleficent.</i></font>

95
00:08:02,378 --> 00:08:05,379
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Katanya itu adalah ciuman cinta sejati.</i></font>

96
00:08:07,894 --> 00:08:10,135
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Namun, Cinta sejatinya
tak berlangsung lama.</i></font>

97
00:08:11,719 --> 00:08:13,520
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Tahun berlalu...</i></font>

98
00:08:13,614 --> 00:08:16,649
<font color="#ffff00"><i>...ambisi Stefan merenggutnya
dari Maleficent.</i></font>

99
00:08:16,876 --> 00:08:20,879
<font color="#ffff00"><i>...dan mendekatkannya
pada kekuasaan.</i></font>

100
00:08:20,993 --> 00:08:24,241
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Sementara Maleficent, yang merupakan
peri terkuat di antara para peri...</i></font>

101
00:08:24,344 --> 00:08:27,944
<font color="#ffff00"><i>...tumbuh menjadi pelindung Kerajaan Moors.</i></font>

102
00:09:14,822 --> 00:09:17,184
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Maleficent terkadang kesepian...</i></font>

103
00:09:17,484 --> 00:09:20,523
<font color="#ffff00"><i>...dan kadang membayangkan
keberadaan Stefan.</i></font>

104
00:09:20,787 --> 00:09:24,733
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Karena dia dulu tak pernah memahami
sikap angkuh dan serakah manusia.</i></font>

105
00:09:25,122 --> 00:09:27,649
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Namun dia belajar.</i></font>

106
00:09:28,091 --> 00:09:32,128
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Karena raja manusia mendengar soal
kekuatan yang tumbuh di Kerajaan Moors.</i></font>

107
00:09:32,352 --> 00:09:35,402
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Dan raja berniat menghancurkannya.</i></font>

108
00:09:55,922 --> 00:09:57,922
<font color="#ffff00">Pasukan, Berhenti!</font>

109
00:09:59,441 --> 00:10:01,179
<font color="#ffff00">Pasukan, Berhenti!</font>

110
00:10:11,850 --> 00:10:13,847
<font color="#ffff00">Ini dia!</font>

111
00:10:14,357 --> 00:10:18,362
<font color="#ffff00">Kerajaan Moors yang misterius,
di mana tak ada yang berani mendekat...</font>

112
00:10:18,413 --> 00:10:22,317
<font color="#ffff00">...karena takut akan sihirnya.</font>

113
00:10:22,345 --> 00:10:24,797
<font color="#ffff00">Tapi aku bilang, mari kita hancurkan!</font>

114
00:10:44,348 --> 00:10:46,844
<font color="#ffff00">Jangan mendekat!</font>

115
00:10:48,031 --> 00:10:51,845
<font color="#ffff00">Raja tak menerima perintah...</font>

116
00:10:51,949 --> 00:10:54,149
<font color="#ffff00">...dari peri bersayap.</font>

117
00:10:55,851 --> 00:10:59,934
<font color="#ffff00">Kau bukan raja bagiku!</font>

118
00:11:05,847 --> 00:11:07,581
<font color="#ffff00">Bunuh dia!</font>

119
00:11:07,682 --> 00:11:09,228
<font color="#ffff00">Pasukan!</font>

120
00:11:13,175 --> 00:11:14,775
<font color="#ffff00">Serang!</font>

121
00:11:19,340 --> 00:11:22,289
<font color="#ffff00">Bangkitlah dan bergabunglah denganku!</font>

122
00:11:27,296 --> 00:11:29,496
<font color="#ffff00">Tahan!</font>

123
00:11:41,709 --> 00:11:43,709
<font color="#ffff00">Itu para makhluk kegelapan!</font>

124
00:12:05,517 --> 00:12:07,825
<font color="#ffff00">Maju!</font>

125
00:13:05,491 --> 00:13:07,017
<font color="#ffff00">Kau!</font>

126
00:13:10,246 --> 00:13:11,990
<font color="#ffff00">Serang demi Raja!</font>

127
00:13:19,154 --> 00:13:22,817
<font color="#ffff00">Kalian takkan bisa mengendalikan
Kerajaan Moors, kapanpun!</font>

128
00:13:22,919 --> 00:13:24,479
<font color="#ffff00">Kau...</font>

129
00:14:02,999 --> 00:14:06,034
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Saat dulu aku diangkat jadi raja...</i></font>

130
00:14:06,837 --> 00:14:11,274
<font color="#ffff00"><i>...aku janji pada rakyatku,
Suatu hari...</i></font>

131
00:14:11,689 --> 00:14:16,180
<font color="#ffff00"><i>...kita akan menguasai Kerajaan
Moors, dan segala isinya...</i></font>

132
00:14:17,285 --> 00:14:20,544
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Kalian semua berjanji...</i></font>

133
00:14:20,627 --> 00:14:25,043
<font color="#ffff00"><i>...untuk mendampingiku
dan akhirnya...</i></font>

134
00:14:30,479 --> 00:14:32,476
<font color="#ffff00">Yang Mulia.</font>

135
00:14:35,502 --> 00:14:38,224
<font color="#ffff00"><i>...kita kalah dalam pertempuran.</i></font>

136
00:14:38,269 --> 00:14:41,864
<font color="#ffff00">Apa inikah warisanku?</font>

137
00:14:42,300 --> 00:14:45,940
<font color="#ffff00">Kalian menunggu kematianku.</font>

138
00:14:46,486 --> 00:14:50,018
<font color="#ffff00">Tak lama lagi, Lalu apa?</font>

139
00:14:50,134 --> 00:14:52,694
<font color="#ffff00">Aku akan pilih penerus...</font>

140
00:14:52,910 --> 00:14:56,697
<font color="#ffff00"><i>...untuk melanjutkan pemerintahan
dan juga menikahi puteriku.</i></font>

141
00:14:57,559 --> 00:15:00,870
<font color="#ffff00">Siapa di antara kalian
yang pantas menggantikanku?</font>

142
00:15:02,099 --> 00:15:05,093
<font color="#ffff00">Bunuh si makhluk bersayap itu!</font>

143
00:15:05,272 --> 00:15:07,322
<font color="#ffff00">Balaskan dendamku!</font>

144
00:15:07,975 --> 00:15:11,375
<font color="#ffff00">Dan setelah kematianku,
Kau akan menggantikanku!</font>

145
00:15:38,666 --> 00:15:40,639
<font color="#ffff00">Maleficent.</font>

146
00:15:41,451 --> 00:15:43,549
<font color="#ffff00">Maleficent!</font>

147
00:15:51,200 --> 00:15:54,622
<font color="#ffff00">Bagaimana kehidupanmu
bersama manusia?</font>

148
00:15:57,107 --> 00:15:59,970
<font color="#ffff00">Maleficent, Aku kemari
untuk memperingatkanmu!</font>

149
00:16:00,681 --> 00:16:02,777
<font color="#ffff00">Mereka ingin membunuhmu!</font>

150
00:16:03,371 --> 00:16:06,277
<font color="#ffff00">Raja Henry takkan berhenti.</font>

151
00:16:08,165 --> 00:16:12,126
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Percayalah padaku.</i></font>

152
00:16:15,314 --> 00:16:17,558
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Mereka bicara banyak hal...</i></font>

153
00:16:17,600 --> 00:16:20,400
<font color="#ffff00"><i>...dan tahun pun berlalu.</i></font>

154
00:16:20,974 --> 00:16:25,115
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Dan dia memaafkan Stefan
atas sikap bodoh serta ambisinya...</i></font>

155
00:16:26,022 --> 00:16:29,785
<font color="#ffff00"><i>...dan semua kejadian di masa lalu.</i></font>

156
00:16:31,890 --> 00:16:33,790
<font color="#ffff00">Kau haus?</font>

157
00:17:08,222 --> 00:17:10,119
<font color="#ffff00">Maleficent?</font>

158
00:19:25,616 --> 00:19:27,199
<font color="#ffff00">Apa-apaan ini?</font>

159
00:19:29,767 --> 00:19:32,568
<font color="#ffff00">Saya telah membalaskan
dendam anda, Tuan.</font>

160
00:19:33,628 --> 00:19:36,110
<font color="#ffff00">Dia sudah ditaklukkan?</font>

161
00:19:38,774 --> 00:19:41,062
<font color="#ffff00">Kerja yang bagus, Nak.</font>

162
00:19:41,089 --> 00:19:43,964
<font color="#ffff00">Kau melakukan apa yang
tak bisa dilakukan yang lain.</font>

163
00:19:44,365 --> 00:19:46,928
<font color="#ffff00">Kau akan menerima balasannya.</font>

164
00:19:48,956 --> 00:19:51,020
<font color="#ffff00">Akan kulakukan yang terbaik...</font>

165
00:19:51,190 --> 00:19:53,915
<font color="#ffff00">...demi jadi penerus yang pantas.</font>

166
00:19:54,059 --> 00:19:55,763
<font color="#ffff00">Yang Mulia.</font>

167
00:22:07,447 --> 00:22:09,095
<font color="#ffff00">Aku menangkapmu!</font>

168
00:22:13,621 --> 00:22:16,211
<font color="#ffff00">Burung nakal. /
Berubah jadi manusia!</font>

169
00:22:29,675 --> 00:22:31,290
<font color="#ffff00">Iblis!</font>

170
00:22:44,658 --> 00:22:47,057
<font color="#ffff00">Apa yang kau perbuat pada diriku?</font>

171
00:22:47,091 --> 00:22:49,767
<font color="#ffff00">Kau lebih ingin dibunuh?</font>

172
00:22:51,062 --> 00:22:54,398
<font color="#ffff00">Tak tahu juga. /
Berhentilah mengeluh.</font>

173
00:22:54,496 --> 00:22:56,582
<font color="#ffff00">Aku telah menyelamatkanmu.</font>

174
00:22:59,396 --> 00:23:01,298
<font color="#ffff00">Maafkan aku.</font>

175
00:23:01,735 --> 00:23:04,251
<font color="#ffff00">Siapa namamu? /
Diaval.</font>

